Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"Those guys" is inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the person I want to present is this.
