Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tsurutaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tsurutaro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:55.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's starting to look like driftwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So thin.
