Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this time I've brought a theory concerning Tsurutaro's body.
