Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce the contestants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,First, with a body fat ratio of 7.2% - literally skin and bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yabe Taro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be a good challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Progressing away from selling her looks, working throughout the industry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...a body that is fully-stacked, but scandalously skinny...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's Kato Sari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's thin but has a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the chest there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite the demerit, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the one taking her on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The flat-chested skinny pole dancer Makino Suteteko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fatigued from all the mental associates, the "mental bag of bones"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...from the comedy duo "Impulse", it's Itakura Toshiyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty ripped, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working out, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The touch of your hands, Tsurutaro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...is freezing! Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And last we have the king of getting in gaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...the skinny yoga master, Kataoka Tsurutaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really showing it off from the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the easiest to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get your feelings of pride, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, look.  It's like you're taking on homeless people.
