Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:29.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...between Yamada-san's house and this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.44,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That'd be scary!
