Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quick about it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is Makino Suteteko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in!  I'm in!
