Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...she is able to progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kato-san has cleared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After this is a succession of clears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then it is finally time for the master Tsurutaro to challenge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty intimidating when you see it right before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,63 years of age and into piercings, the veteran senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:53.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...makes his way into the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The yoga master takes his extreme trained body and advances on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yogi Tsurutaro has cleared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels strangely satisfying to make it out, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like being reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So here we have level 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in Atami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really necessary to come all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...if we hadn't come all the way to Atami, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:37.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so we come to the second stage in Atami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait wait wait...
