Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Unable to move freely in the tight space, he reaches his limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is unable to use his lifting power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't bend your legs in a space like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give...I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:14.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The top ace Yabe Taro reaches his limit and retires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:19.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finally the Yoga Master is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:39.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The expert of nauli aims to clear the final challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:39.00,Translator Notes,,0,0,0,,T/N: Nauli is a yoga movement involving massaging the internal belly organs in a circular motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This part is only 8cm wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But here...my ribs are holding me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:48.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He slides in with zero effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.20,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:55.50,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's over 60!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be able to do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:15.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He makes his move in going upwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:28.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so, thanks to his years of expert training in yoga...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:32.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...he is able to move his body upwards, even in such a confined space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the nauli.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!  He has conquered all of the courses!  Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kataoka Tsurutaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:55.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tsurutaro clears the final course and confirms...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:58.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...he is the best at traversing tight gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a winning nauli!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an amazing nauli!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:08.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So, if you can nauli, you can clear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:10.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He proved it true!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a veteran star of our company!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.53,0:23:21.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,In a place I used to live in a few years back...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:24.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...it got burgled by someone, and they got in through a small gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:27.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It must have been that old git!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have known nauli.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:31.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ah, I called him an "old git"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an honorable senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:36.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That nauli is something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed he got out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone at the company wanted him to refuse, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:44.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was better than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, with the first location in Tsukishima. Downtown, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:49.97,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:51.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, when you were filming "Downtown Now" out of the studio in Odaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...when Tsurutaro came on as a guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:24:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...it was that store's gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The store on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:05.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's a coinincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.99,0:24:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.49,0:24:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, on a Downtown program with Tsurotaro-san as a guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you change the staff, this is what the content turns into.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.73,0:24:18.34,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Our next presenter is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.71,0:24:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:26.64,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Please welcome Hakata Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.24,0:24:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.38,0:24:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'd like to ask all of you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.85,0:24:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering all of the people you know, including friends and the like...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.42,0:24:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...how tall is the tallest person you know? What would you say, Kawakita?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.25,0:24:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,185 cm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.56,0:24:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.36,0:24:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.03,0:24:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that person play sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.63,0:24:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He plays basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.29,0:24:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so he plays basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.46,0:24:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Jinnai?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.80,0:24:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it would have to be Koyabu, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.87,0:24:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's about...189 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.34,0:24:54.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No, well, wouldn't it be Onigiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:24:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Onigiri, a younger comedian in Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.74,0:24:57.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be Onigiri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.51,0:25:00.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A former volleyball player.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.48,0:25:02.01,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's 190 and...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.01,0:25:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out that he is 193cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.81,0:25:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's big, ain't he.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.92,0:25:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So this time, I've brought a tall person theory, which is...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.95,0:25:13.39,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There exists someone over 2m who is "culturally inclined."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.09,0:25:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what do I mean by "culturally inclined"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.76,0:25:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that in school clubs and the like...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.80,0:25:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...they never played sports or did athletics.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.43,0:25:24.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They didn't move their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.10,0:25:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, the theory is that no 2m person is in the "going home club."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.94,0:25:29.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They didn't do that, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.41,0:25:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think an important point here is even if you didn't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.81,0:25:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...the people around you would force you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.28,0:25:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that this pattern is common...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...but is it true of all people more than 2m tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.88,0:25:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also an image that tall people don't like fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.52,0:25:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and cultural clubs don't recruit as aggressively as sports clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.86,0:25:51.93,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.83,0:25:58.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory: There exists someone over 2m tall who is culturally inclined.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.24,0:26:03.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We come now to Kato Shipping, a logistics company.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.07,0:26:10.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The boss is so tall that his head can be seen from another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.64,0:26:08.71,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What the heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.58,0:26:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: How tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.58,0:26:12.82,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Expensive suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.98,0:26:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 2 meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.65,0:26:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,2 meters tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.05,0:26:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. 2 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.85,0:26:17.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,WOW. LARGE.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.25,0:26:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Have you been a big guy since you were young?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.82,0:26:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When I graduated middle school, I was 190cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.99,0:26:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was 2m when I graduated high school, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.53,0:26:25.20,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,But was he involved\Nin sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.13,0:26:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might end up around 220cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.40,0:26:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I used to play volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.53,0:26:29.00,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah, volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.00,0:26:30.57,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah, volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.17,0:26:31.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Right, this is him in 1992...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.13,0:26:35.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...appearing at the Barcelona Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.77,0:26:33.64,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's the dream, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.64,0:26:35.34,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The dream indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.61,0:26:40.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A former representative on Team Japan, Minami Katsuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.91,0:26:45.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So of course he has sports experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.38,0:26:49.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An absolutely electrifying 2m athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.19,0:26:53.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We then come to see the workers at this pharmacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.06,0:26:57.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this 2m tall pharmacist, Hanashio Kaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.69,0:26:59.06,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,A pharmacist?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.06,0:27:00.43,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.40,0:27:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Do you have any sports experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I did play basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.27,0:27:03.63,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.93,0:27:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I played from about fourth grade until college.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.14,0:27:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I played for about 12 years, all told.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.67,0:27:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Why did you aim to become a pharmacist?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.74,0:27:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had no talent, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.21,0:27:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wasn't very coordinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.11,0:27:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was better at studying, plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.78,0:27:17.35,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.18,0:27:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was good at chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.22,0:27:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to go in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.42,0:27:26.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was originally more culturally inclined...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.16,0:27:32.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...but because of his height he played basketball all the way through to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.63,0:27:38.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now, this 2m+ university student.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.40,0:27:39.00,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow, a Benz.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.30,0:27:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,From first grade to my first year of college, I played basketball all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.27,0:27:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: And did you have a reason to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.31,0:27:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I got bored of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.01,0:27:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be good if I didn't go pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.71,0:27:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.65,0:27:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: What is life like at 202cm?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.45,0:27:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Do you have any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.79,0:28:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's full of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.92,0:28:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, you might be with a friend in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.06,0:28:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great meeting up because they can find you easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.13,0:28:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I've been used as a landmark for people to meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.60,0:28:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like "There's a crazy tall dude by me in Shibuya!"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.47,0:28:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll move a little closer to that guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.01,0:28:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll be there"...I've heard phone calls like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.81,0:28:18.28,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He sticks out \Nlike a scarecrow
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.28,0:28:20.78,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He is tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.28,0:28:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because I'm narrow-minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.15,0:28:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I find it frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.08,0:28:29.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now this 205cm person working at a construction company.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.72,0:28:34.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In 2008, he appeared at the Beijing Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.09,0:28:37.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An ex-volleyball player.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.43,0:28:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Why do you think you've grown so tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.03,0:28:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case, my parents were both tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.43,0:28:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad is 185cm, mom is 175 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.17,0:28:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My younger sister is 186 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.24,0:28:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: 186cm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.87,0:28:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My great-grandfather was 190cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.48,0:28:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard no clothes would fit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.85,0:29:02.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are basketball and volleyball players over 2m.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.72,0:29:04.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.72,0:29:10.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...in Tottori, we found a soccer player over 2m.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.56,0:29:14.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On the Gainare Tottori team...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:19.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...a 205cm J-Leaguer: Hatanaka Makito.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.20,0:29:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff) How long have you been playing soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.64,0:29:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I started in first grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.97,0:29:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I played basketball and volleyball, since I was often invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.64,0:29:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, I really liked soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.11,0:29:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: In soccer, what is good about being taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.45,0:29:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In formation, for corner and free kicks...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.05,0:29:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...you have a higher chance when you're in a group of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.49,0:29:46.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then we have this 2m soccer player...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.66,0:29:49.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...who attends Hosei University.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.00,0:29:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a goalkeeper, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.13,0:29:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...the ball comes in high.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.87,0:29:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of taking high goals head-on...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.01,0:29:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think I need the height.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.74,0:30:02.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And this survey revealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.71,0:30:03.71,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,TEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.08,0:30:07.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...the sports people over 2m do most frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.18,0:30:11.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected, basketball and volleyball take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.99,0:30:17.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now we'll look at the maximum height of Japanese athletes from various sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.60,0:30:20.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First, basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.60,0:30:25.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Okayama Yasutaka, who was 227cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.20,0:30:28.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was also selected for the NBA draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.41,0:30:34.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is currently the tallest Japanese person.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.24,0:30:35.91,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.15,0:30:37.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then, volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.08,0:30:41.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Otake Hideyuki, 208cm
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.95,0:30:44.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Currently the tallest person to represent Japan at an Olympic games...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.65,0:30:49.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...with the tallest ever height in any sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.59,0:30:49.76,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.93,0:30:52.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.83,0:30:55.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Baba Shouhei, 209cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.87,0:30:58.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Later known as Giant Baba.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.54,0:31:02.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of Japanese pro baseballers over 2m...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.87,0:31:05.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...there has only been Baba.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.81,0:31:08.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Continuing now with sumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.05,0:31:13.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Akashi Shiranosuke, 252 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.35,0:31:14.82,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.92,0:31:14.82,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.65,0:31:18.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Japan Sumo Association has recognized him as the first yokozuna
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.39,0:31:17.59,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.59,0:31:20.89,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Can't be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.86,0:31:22.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...but we don't know when he lived, or if he really even existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.69,0:31:27.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are many unclear parts. It's legendary history.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.10,0:31:27.63,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Did he really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.30,0:31:32.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, we'll check the maximum heights...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.70,0:31:36.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...of some sports where being tall might be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.11,0:31:39.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Table Tennis
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.01,0:31:43.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Muramatsu Yuuto, 180 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.45,0:31:46.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gymnastics
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.22,0:31:51.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tsukamoto Junki, 178 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.36,0:31:54.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Marathon
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.26,0:31:59.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Horibata Hiroyuki, 189 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.10,0:32:02.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Figure Skating
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.07,0:32:06.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Hiroshi, 180cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.40,0:32:11.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No one here is taller than 2m.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.74,0:32:16.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So, if you are looking for someone over 2m who is culturally inclined...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.14,0:32:16.81,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right, that was\Nthe main topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.98,0:32:18.52,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.71,0:32:21.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The person we found with the shortest history in sports...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.52,0:32:26.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...was the swimming instructor of this gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.46,0:32:31.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,206 cm Fukazawa Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.66,0:32:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Did you always do aquatics?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.56,0:32:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I started from baby swimming at 0 years old and swam until 8th grade
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.17,0:32:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Is it an advantage in swimming if you're taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.34,0:32:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.04,0:32:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When I jump in...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.14,0:32:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can get ahead of everyone because of my height.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.35,0:32:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands are big...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.48,0:32:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...and my feet are also big...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.59,0:33:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can push more water out of the way. It is advantageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.96,0:33:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Did you do other sports after you quit swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.90,0:33:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I did basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.70,0:33:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a recommendation to go to Akita Prefecture's...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.50,0:33:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...Noshiro Industrial High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.14,0:33:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit on the court..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.27,0:33:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I dropped out in my second year of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.57,0:33:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: You dropped out of high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.98,0:33:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped out, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.24,0:33:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a middle school graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.05,0:33:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: You didn't go back to high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.95,0:33:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.78,0:33:32.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Result: There are no culturally inclined people over 2m, but there are 2m tall middle school graduates.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.22,0:33:35.43,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So there really weren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.43,0:33:37.69,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There aren't any, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.43,0:33:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.69,0:33:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one with the shallowest sports history.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.50,0:33:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot of things from this survey of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.10,0:33:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Being born with a height of 2m or more...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.17,0:33:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...decides your life's path, to a degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.77,0:33:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you'll always end up doing sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.31,0:33:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We put together a spectrum of different lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.01,0:33:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...and put it into a VTR...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.85,0:34:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Hamada laughed a lot at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.95,0:34:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He really laughed a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.52,0:34:05.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Here's our next presenter, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.66,0:34:17.47,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Tamura Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.80,0:34:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.90,0:34:19.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Aren't you doing "everyone's theory"..?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.84,0:34:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today, Hamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.84,0:34:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember that fun thing has begun?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.41,0:34:26.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It goes on?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.04,0:34:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It started last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.48,0:34:30.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is it really ok to call it "fun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.08,0:34:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.25,0:34:34.25,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think it's frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.82,0:34:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You do? I do too actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.25,0:34:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's this:
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.09,0:34:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our project about six men and women living in a shared house and experiencing love.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.90,0:34:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And see if love sparks between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.30,0:34:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That usually happens.\NIt does.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.53,0:34:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I said there are six participants...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.32,0:34:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...but one of them is actually Kuro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.61,0:35:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's actually a love-reality with five sparkling young boys and girls and Kuro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.21,0:35:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What love can there be with Kuro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:06.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Everyone's serious about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.45,0:35:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They are, and the whole show is still in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.69,0:35:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From which point of view should we watch this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.42,0:35:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what we saw last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.56,0:35:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...was almost horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.29,0:35:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if that's the first time you're watching this, here's a quick and easy recap from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.43,0:35:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our six participants have started \Nliving together inside this shared house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.04,0:35:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On their second day, they had a barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.24,0:35:36.11,Hamada,,0,0,0,,And all the girls wore swimsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.48,0:35:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They wore swimsuits, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.11,0:35:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kuro-chan looked at them with some frightful eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.08,0:35:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan also got alone together with a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.79,0:35:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and confessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.96,0:35:48.79,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Two of them, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.79,0:35:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Jinnai.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.93,0:35:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he knows everything is getting recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.86,0:35:53.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.50,0:35:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, he went for two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.60,0:35:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.17,0:35:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.57,0:36:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know maybe I shouldn't say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think that I like you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.54,0:36:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...I like you the best, for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.21,0:36:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I've decided to be honest with my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.68,0:36:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one I like the most, Ran-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.15,0:36:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rion-chan and Ran-chan are interested in Taiga-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.62,0:36:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiga-kun is a 20 years old good looking man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.23,0:36:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But he never actually dated anyone before, \Nso of course he's never had his first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.33,0:36:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never kissed a girl before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.03,0:36:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if Kuro-chan wasn't there, \Neverything would have gone so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.10,0:36:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hating on him already?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.14,0:36:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan? Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.04,0:36:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a miracle could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.78,0:36:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... it won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.51,0:36:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He did all of that even though he knows he's going on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.19,0:36:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what are his chances of success?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.12,0:36:53.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the girls haven't see it on-air yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.96,0:36:56.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So he knows they can't find it out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.80,0:37:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you usually have for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.07,0:37:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fruits or a smoothie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.90,0:37:07.20,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.24,0:37:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.20,0:37:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been thinking about my health and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.61,0:37:11.57,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.17,0:37:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trending recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.18,0:37:14.21,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's trying to impress her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.21,0:37:16.71,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No way he drinks\N smoothies.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.15,0:37:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, where are you two off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.26,0:37:19.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,"You two"...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.02,0:37:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To Kawagoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.62,0:37:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.12,0:37:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.32,0:37:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.72,0:37:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.62,0:37:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.19,0:37:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.29,0:37:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.89,0:37:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.99,0:37:31.13,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.93,0:37:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing something today, Ran-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.26,0:37:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about going to grab a bite with Taiga tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.13,0:37:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.30,0:37:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.77,0:37:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you didn't ask me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.37,0:37:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to be asked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.17,0:37:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.21,0:37:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.34,0:37:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.68,0:37:51.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's really disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.71,0:37:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.78,0:37:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You were all about Rion-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.15,0:37:54.72,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's already fed \Nup with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.72,0:37:56.32,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's being exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.42,0:37:59.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's going for both \Nof them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.18,0:37:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh, I told you right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.32,0:37:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rion-chan is a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.75,0:37:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.52,0:38:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's the boundary line on who you can call a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.33,0:38:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A boundary line on friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.10,0:38:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's about I would kiss them or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.03,0:38:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you say it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.34,0:38:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...even if you don't want to date someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.54,0:38:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...can you kiss them? Can you hold their hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.34,0:38:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.54,0:38:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.87,0:38:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You meant that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.48,0:38:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say, if I don't like her, I can't kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.68,0:38:26.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It began.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.65,0:38:31.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?\NAll these flashy images...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.59,0:38:35.02,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause they're\N fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.29,0:38:35.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It surely is fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.29,0:38:38.39,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,There's not a single time\NKuro-chan appeared here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.39,0:38:39.96,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.96,0:38:42.47,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,At this point it's still good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.47,0:38:44.40,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is good.\NShe's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.20,0:38:47.10,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.74,0:38:51.74,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.34,0:38:54.14,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Is he doing pachinko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.14,0:38:57.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Don't look at other's\N won balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.32,0:39:04.52,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that\Nfootage of him looking\Nat the pachinko balls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.49,0:39:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Toki-no-Kane (bell of time).
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.92,0:39:09.66,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.62,0:39:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki-no-Kane?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.03,0:39:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.60,0:39:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Hand towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.83,0:39:16.17,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's a nice date.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.76,0:39:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.47,0:39:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.73,0:39:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.43,0:39:21.10,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This part seems to belong\Nto a different tv show.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.10,0:39:24.37,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,"A different show" what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.37,0:39:26.04,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is so wholesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.04,0:39:29.08,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,These two are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.11,0:39:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.34,0:39:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.48,0:39:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a footbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.58,0:39:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.25,0:39:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.05,0:39:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.48,0:39:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about Kuro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.19,0:39:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a cute character, I mean, the way he moves around, his high pitch, he's cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.76,0:39:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think his personality is really good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.13,0:39:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he really looks like a... middle aged man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rion-chan sorry, I was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.20,0:39:51.93,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He said he's old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.23,0:39:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.07,0:39:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.64,0:39:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kinda black-themed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.24,0:39:57.24,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,She clearly did!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.41,0:39:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's because you're Kuro-chan (kuro = black)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.77,0:39:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? For that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.91,0:40:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I chose black.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.21,0:40:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a double-Kuro-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.21,0:40:03.14,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They got an appointment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.18,0:40:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.38,0:40:04.61,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.61,0:40:06.61,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Eh? They're on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.85,0:40:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to a place? I have it reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.58,0:40:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.22,0:40:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, it's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.68,0:40:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a reservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.72,0:40:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.25,0:40:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's to Kuro-chan and Rion's first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.16,0:40:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.29,0:40:18.29,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to watch\N this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.29,0:40:19.46,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really, who can?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.46,0:40:22.93,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\Nshould I watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.96,0:40:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.53,0:40:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.50,0:40:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I know I was going to meet you today...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.17,0:40:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I thought this could make you happy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.14,0:40:30.14,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,If this guy gets drunk\Nit's gonna be awful
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.07,0:40:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.64,0:40:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.74,0:40:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.88,0:40:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so cute! What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.75,0:40:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.30,0:40:37.55,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is actually cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.55,0:40:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.45,0:40:41.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It must feel good to\Nreceive one of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.18,0:40:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a candy bouquet
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.68,0:40:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Candy bouquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.59,0:40:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're an "R", is it for "Rion"?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.99,0:40:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,An "R", of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.09,0:40:49.29,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Can he do such things?\N- It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.06,0:40:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.66,0:40:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never received something like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.56,0:40:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.03,0:40:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that makes me the first one...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.90,0:40:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...to ever give you a candy bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.83,0:40:57.10,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.10,0:40:59.10,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ugh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.70,0:41:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.37,0:41:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It really looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.44,0:41:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.04,0:41:03.07,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.31,0:41:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.34,0:41:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.11,0:41:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But even the lunch you made was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.51,0:41:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.31,0:41:12.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.42,0:41:15.62,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's sweating so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.75,0:41:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, since when...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.08,0:41:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when did you start being intersted in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.82,0:41:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.04,0:41:21.17,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The hell is this guy?\NHe pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.89,0:41:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...when we first met, I thought you were so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.23,0:41:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.86,0:41:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was like, "I want to ask her out".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.03,0:41:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.80,0:41:31.90,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,But he's intersted in\Nlike, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.67,0:41:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because I wanted to make princess Rion happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.00,0:41:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.00,0:41:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.91,0:41:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...a really touching thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.11,0:41:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.08,0:41:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...I really want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.88,0:41:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...protect you, Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.09,0:41:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.79,0:41:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.42,0:41:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really nice, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.06,0:41:55.06,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Protect her from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.22,0:41:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The image I had of you totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.73,0:41:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I've been called a liar since last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.83,0:42:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.60,0:42:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I never told a lie which could hurt other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.97,0:42:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.30,0:42:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're being tricked often,\N you've never tricked anyone yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.01,0:42:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's because I don't want to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.64,0:42:16.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Maybe this girl\Nis strange too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.64,0:42:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if I'm so blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.81,0:42:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.85,0:42:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me pat your head a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.25,0:42:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.62,0:42:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reaction was really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.22,0:42:22.62,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.49,0:42:26.19,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I don't really know\Nhow to watch this
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.19,0:42:28.32,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,How should I \Nwatch this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.32,0:42:30.32,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Should I root for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.79,0:42:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been treated like this before so... I'm kinda happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.80,0:42:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.90,0:42:42.14,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh, I feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.14,0:42:46.64,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The big sis is going\Nafter the younger boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.20,0:42:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.51,0:42:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.84,0:42:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think about...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.64,0:42:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan?\N- Kuro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.38,0:42:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.85,0:42:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time he went and told me like "you're good"...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.32,0:42:55.78,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,She said it \Nloud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.29,0:43:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been told that and I really wish he would stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.29,0:43:07.30,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to be\Nmuch interested in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.69,0:43:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.46,0:43:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... I think you're nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.30,0:43:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.46,0:43:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For real? Alright! I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.70,0:43:13.14,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.94,0:43:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dinner was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.07,0:43:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.31,0:43:20.88,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This girl picked \Nthe wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.88,0:43:22.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No need to say\N that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.85,0:43:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! This...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.55,0:43:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.31,0:43:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, so dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.95,0:43:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah it's amazing, it's a 360 degrees panoramic view.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.85,0:43:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.22,0:43:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.89,0:43:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.41,0:43:37.93,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Too fast, too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.93,0:43:38.91,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san?\N{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HF60919&}- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.91,0:43:40.70,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Do you think he's \Ngonna assault her?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.70,0:43:44.90,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,For real, though\Nhe's really rushing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.40,0:43:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh look, we're holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.33,0:43:48.97,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What if... he's actually\Ngood at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.97,0:43:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you can see everything from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.21,0:43:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...all I want to look at is you, Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.34,0:43:57.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Kuro-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.05,0:43:57.65,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's drawing closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.65,0:44:00.72,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,For real? This\Nis impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.72,0:44:02.72,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's getting\Ncloser and closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.65,0:44:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.25,0:44:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.92,0:44:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to say what I'm feeling, so now...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.59,0:44:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I've come to a point in \Nwhich you're to only person I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.46,0:44:14.10,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Way too fast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.10,0:44:17.73,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's that way of\Nsaying it? Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.86,0:44:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.50,0:44:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you need some rehab?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.42,0:44:19.79,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The hell is he sayin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.34,0:44:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when you meet someone you can feel nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.14,0:44:23.84,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The hell is he\Ntalking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.47,0:44:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's really important to look into each other's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.54,0:44:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should practice it some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.64,0:44:27.74,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.88,0:44:32.38,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is unbearable!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.38,0:44:34.38,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh man, oh man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.74,0:44:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.38,0:44:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.08,0:44:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you some rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.35,0:44:37.65,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The hell is he doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.65,0:44:39.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What are you doing,\NKuro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.02,0:44:41.49,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is rehab!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.02,0:44:41.49,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,- Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.76,0:44:43.49,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.69,0:44:47.26,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Uwaah! Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.90,0:44:47.26,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,See? Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.26,0:44:49.26,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What is he doing..?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.07,0:44:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't surprise me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.97,0:44:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By "rehab" you meant this rehab?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.61,0:44:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what you meant by that, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.24,0:45:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.24,0:45:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was nervous, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.68,0:45:02.68,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.04,0:45:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, it caught me off guard, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.71,0:45:06.12,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's really creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.02,0:45:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You still need some rehab, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.05,0:45:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.35,0:45:15.89,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I'm actually sweating\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.46,0:45:15.89,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.89,0:45:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.66,0:45:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been in such places before.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.66,0:45:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, in such fancy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.47,0:45:26.54,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This all revolves\Naround fanciness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.20,0:45:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit tired, maybe because I ate so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.11,0:45:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be the alcohol flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.61,0:45:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.94,0:45:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.08,0:45:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit drunk myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.71,0:45:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.48,0:45:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when I get to...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.55,0:45:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...have a drink with someone I like or such...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.69,0:45:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then I get drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.89,0:45:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...I start feeling like I want to kiss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.30,0:45:54.66,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ran-chan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.20,0:45:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.20,0:45:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.66,0:45:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.67,0:45:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.33,0:46:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's just that and...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.00,0:46:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.41,0:46:06.71,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.71,0:46:08.14,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.14,0:46:09.58,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.81,0:46:12.18,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That was his\Nfirst kiss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.18,0:46:15.18,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.38,0:46:15.18,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He got assaulted!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.18,0:46:17.82,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What an unexpected\Nturn of events...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.82,0:46:20.26,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,She does that and\Nleaves like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.45,0:46:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit the convenience store and then I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.12,0:46:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.29,0:46:24.56,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He is perplexed!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.29,0:46:24.56,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This guy's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.56,0:46:28.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,His face was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.97,0:46:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? What a huge shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.24,0:46:35.97,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He was so stiff like "what just happened?"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.97,0:46:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.97,0:46:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...Taiga's first kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.54,0:46:39.74,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.97,0:46:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.74,0:46:42.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was rather awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.91,0:46:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so stiff, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.34,0:46:45.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I mean, normal, proper people are like... slower? You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.78,0:46:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...slower, yes of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.42,0:46:47.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Development-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.58,0:46:50.39,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What the hell is "proper people" supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.39,0:46:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are developing so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.82,0:46:52.86,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.86,0:46:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.32,0:46:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a slow attacker, Hamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.39,0:46:58.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.83,0:47:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.30,0:47:00.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.46,0:47:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.63,0:47:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you think about that... \Nthere are just two guys, right? So...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.73,0:47:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're not counting Kuro-chan, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.90,0:47:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You straight up excluded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.11,0:47:13.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You were saying "gross, gross" too much before!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.57,0:47:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there are only two possible guys for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.58,0:47:15.74,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You've said the harshest things!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.74,0:47:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But really...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.11,0:47:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there could be tension between the girls\N'cause they may want to aim at one of the two guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.25,0:47:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, but don't you think Kuro-chan \Nand Rion date felt genuinely nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.99,0:47:32.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We can't know until we watch the rest, she may\Nnever come back to Monster House after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.96,0:47:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be mentally shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.10,0:47:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how will the love life of our six participants go on?\NThere's still more to watch now!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.97,0:47:41.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's more of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.47,0:47:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.04,0:47:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's the share house?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.24,0:47:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Its atmosphere is really great...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.35,0:47:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...'cause I get to live with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.21,0:47:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.22,0:47:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd know if you were inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.60,0:47:55.17,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.35,0:47:57.69,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.69,0:47:59.76,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's his favorite\Njunior colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.39,0:48:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rion's pajama were really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.72,0:48:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.22,0:48:04.26,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This suddenly \Nfeels like a skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.93,0:48:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.03,0:48:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.06,0:48:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.61,0:48:06.36,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.36,0:48:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to take one while pretending \Nto take a selfie, but I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.50,0:48:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.73,0:48:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So a pretend-selfie... for sneak photography?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.20,0:48:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not sneak photography.\NI need it as data.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.84,0:48:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Data?\N - Yes, material.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.17,0:48:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can remember more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.84,0:48:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, if she changes hairstyle or such...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.38,0:48:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can look at the photo and be like "oh, yesterday they weren't like this". I can tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.59,0:48:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.32,0:48:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.32,0:48:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.86,0:48:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.22,0:48:38.09,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is seriously\Nvoyeurism!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.09,0:48:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It even makes sound when I take one, I should set it to mute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.30,0:48:45.33,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.10,0:48:44.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.93,0:48:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is there someone you like in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.14,0:48:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest I'm currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.81,0:48:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...interested in both Rion and Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.21,0:48:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But which one of them is your first choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.65,0:48:59.05,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.52,0:49:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment it's Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.72,0:49:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.45,0:49:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I really started to like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.66,0:49:09.46,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.79,0:49:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to change her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.93,0:49:14.43,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.03,0:49:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like Rion's face and...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.43,0:49:19.44,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He should date\Nthis dude instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.73,0:49:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.60,0:49:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...she seems kinda dumb, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.17,0:49:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I even went on a date with her
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.47,0:49:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.21,0:49:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.27,0:49:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't make it on my first date, but I think on\N our next one I'm positive I'll get a kiss from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.65,0:49:33.55,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Is he for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.35,0:49:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to get your hands on both of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.55,0:49:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.72,0:49:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah I mean that, if it goes well...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.79,0:49:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if they find you out...?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.99,0:49:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more like "they're both good"...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.39,0:49:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If Rion-chan does...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.83,0:49:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can manage to find a way out of it by talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.06,0:49:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...about Ran-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.40,0:49:53.40,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This guy is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.60,0:49:55.17,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.17,0:49:58.04,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.31,0:49:58.04,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's really the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.90,0:49:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She really seems to be strong willed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.83,0:49:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think she's softer on such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.87,0:49:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.91,0:50:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.54,0:50:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.24,0:50:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.65,0:50:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no one's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.65,0:50:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only Taiga, he's watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.65,0:50:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you playing guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.52,0:50:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.59,0:50:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.49,0:50:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.35,0:50:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...been on a date with Ayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.92,0:50:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to Kawagoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.89,0:50:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Kawagoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.66,0:50:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, about Kuro-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.20,0:50:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You had dinner with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.86,0:50:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.20,0:50:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.23,0:50:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal I guess, we had lots of conversation, \Nhe then said stuff like "I'll protect you".
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.61,0:50:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was kind of... heartening I guess...?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.34,0:50:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.08,0:50:36.25,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He kind of made\Nan impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.34,0:50:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it nice overall?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.81,0:50:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, it kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.12,0:50:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.55,0:50:40.25,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Say the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.45,0:50:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm overthinking it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.56,0:50:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...it felt like he was about to kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.22,0:50:49.93,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,She said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.86,0:50:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is difficult to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.29,0:50:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I say this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.00,0:50:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,His mouth really stunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.23,0:51:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.10,0:51:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was something out of this world... like a rotten egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.31,0:51:07.98,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I had no idea!!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.98,0:51:11.18,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,But such thing\Nwas so obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.01,0:51:04.64,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.14,0:51:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a rotten egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.14,0:51:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.21,0:51:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Like those you forgot to dispose of.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.35,0:51:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Rion-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.45,0:51:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...about Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.42,0:51:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.49,0:51:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's simply cool, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.06,0:51:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...I mean, I think of him like a guy I'd be interested in...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.73,0:51:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I'd like to talk to him alone some more, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.73,0:51:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.20,0:51:34.63,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Taiga, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.41,0:51:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.54,0:51:38.97,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.97,0:51:41.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,With a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.14,0:51:41.28,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's for his \Nstinky mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.28,0:51:44.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,There's an hell\Nunder that mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.28,0:51:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.71,0:51:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.25,0:51:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I had dinner with my junior colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.08,0:51:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.95,0:51:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.65,0:51:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You had dinner with Ran-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.89,0:51:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.09,0:51:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.89,0:51:57.83,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.43,0:51:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.43,0:51:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.83,0:52:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well of course it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.33,0:52:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.53,0:52:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did you two go?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.00,0:52:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you'll tell everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.04,0:52:09.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why does he\Nwant to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.41,0:52:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.74,0:52:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not a loose tongue like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.38,0:52:17.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,His tongue is\Nloose, we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.52,0:52:21.25,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It also stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.91,0:52:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok but... don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.32,0:52:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.49,0:52:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We... kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.72,0:52:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You kissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.93,0:52:31.46,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.00,0:52:38.33,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's unfair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.59,0:52:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it actually came from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.00,0:52:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.00,0:52:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.27,0:52:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.74,0:52:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said you were interested in Rion-chan, \Ndoes it mean you're done with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.61,0:52:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really know it myself yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.34,0:52:47.64,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.71,0:52:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It may sound bad but...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.81,0:52:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...I haven't decided yet, I don't know what to feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.81,0:52:54.58,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's puzzled.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.58,0:52:56.58,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Of course he is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.95,0:52:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.32,0:52:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't think it's good to two-time a girl.
