Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.92,0:53:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you two-time a girl, you'll end up hurting both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.16,0:53:02.16,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Are you for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.52,0:53:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only possible outcome.
